msgid "See the :doc:`features` for examples and highlights."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:32
msgid ""
"Get spack from the `github repository <https://github.com/spack/spack>`_ and "
"install your first package:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:36
msgid ""
"$ git clone -c feature.manyFiles=true --depth=2 https://github.com/spack/"
"spack.git\n"
"$ cd spack/bin\n"
"$ ./spack install libelf"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:43
msgid ""
"``-c feature.manyFiles=true`` improves git's performance on repositories "
"with 1,000+ files."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:45
msgid ""
"``--depth=2`` prunes the git history to reduce the size of the Spack "
"installation."
msgstr ""

